---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Customer Testimonials | Woodstyle Joinery Carlisle"
  description="Read what our customers say about Woodstyle Joinery's craftsmanship and service. Real reviews from satisfied clients across Carlisle and Cumbria."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero text-center py-12 mb-12">
    <div class="container py-6" data-reveal>
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">In Their Words</span>
      <h1 class="display-5 font-bold">Testimonials</h1>
      <p class="lead mx-auto mb-0" style="max-width: 640px">
        Words from customers who trusted Woodstyle Joinery with their homes and gardens
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="container pb-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">

      <!-- Testimonial -->
      <div data-reveal>
        <article class="testimonial-card">
          <h3>Summerhouse</h3>
          <blockquote class="border-l-4 ps-6 italic mt-6">
            To Alan and the team, thanks very much for a great job done on our
            summerhouse. It looks great – just shame about the weather!
            <span class="block mt-2 font-semibold">— Paul & Michelle</span>
          </blockquote>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal>
        <article class="testimonial-card">
          <h3>Wood Stores</h3>
          <blockquote class="border-l-4 ps-6 italic mt-6">
            Thank you for making the wood stores so quickly for us.
            <span class="block mt-2 font-semibold">— Phillipa</span>
          </blockquote>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal>
        <article class="testimonial-card">
          <h3>Bespoke Joinery</h3>
          <blockquote class="border-l-4 ps-6 italic mt-6">
            To Alan, thank you for putting up with me and all my demands — but I’m
            sure you’ll agree now it’s finished, it looks great! I love it.
            <span class="block mt-2 font-semibold">— Angela</span>
          </blockquote>
        </article>
      </div>

      <!-- Image Testimonial -->
      <div data-reveal>
        <article class="testimonial-card testimonial-with-image">
          <div class="testimonial-grid">
            <img
              src="/images/testimonials/cornwall-log-store.jpg"
              alt="Cornwall Log Store by Woodstyle Joinery"
              class="testimonial-image"
            />

            <div>
              <h3>Cornwall Log Store</h3>
              <blockquote class="border-l-4 ps-6 italic mt-6">
                We have a house in Cornwall and I used Woodstyle because of the
                design. I particularly liked the oak front and tiled roof. The
                young person who came to construct it was charming, hardworking,
                and very tidy. I have no hesitation in recommending both the
                product and the service — they are excellent.
                <span class="block mt-2 font-semibold">— Alan</span>
              </blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal>
        <article class="testimonial-card">
          <h3>Woodland Log Shed</h3>
          <blockquote class="border-l-4 ps-6 italic mt-6">
            Thank you so much for moving the log shed into the wood for us. The
            house is sold now. We hope to build opposite and will definitely
            come back to you.
            <span class="block mt-2 font-semibold">— Sue</span>
          </blockquote>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal>
        <article class="testimonial-card">
          <h3>Oak Log Store & Conservatory</h3>
          <blockquote class="border-l-4 ps-6 italic mt-6">
            Our initial purchase was an oak log store, which was beautifully made
            and much admired. Over the years, Woodstyle has completed several
            projects for us, including replacing our conservatory with a
            traditional oak frame and slate roof. The result is a stunning,
            comfortable space we can use all year round. We cannot speak highly
            enough of the quality, efficiency, and courtesy throughout.
            <span class="block mt-2 font-semibold">— Peter</span>
          </blockquote>
        </article>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.testimonial-card {
  position: relative;
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  padding: 2.5rem;
  height: 100%;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-xs);
  transition: transform 0.3s var(--ease-out), box-shadow 0.3s var(--ease), border-color 0.3s var(--ease);
}

.testimonial-card::before {
  content: "\201C";
  position: absolute;
  top: 0.6rem;
  right: 1.4rem;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 4.5rem;
  line-height: 1;
  color: var(--accent);
  opacity: 0.16;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.testimonial-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  border-color: transparent;
}

.testimonial-card h3 {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--ink);
  position: relative;
  display: inline-block;
  padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.testimonial-card h3::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  width: 36px;
  height: 3px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  background: var(--accent);
}

.testimonial-card blockquote {
  border-color: var(--secondary) !important;
  color: var(--ink-muted);
}

.testimonial-with-image {
  padding: 2rem;
}

.testimonial-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
  gap: 2rem;
  align-items: center;
}

.testimonial-image {
  width: 100%;
  height: 180px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .testimonial-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .testimonial-image {
    height: 220px;
  }
}
</style>
